    <section>
        <a href="/singapore/the-straits-times/textview" title="The Straits Times">The Straits Times</a>
        - <a href="/singapore/the-straits-times/20200821/textview" title="The Straits Times - 2020-08-21"><time>2020-08-21</time></a>
        - <span>LIFE | STYLE</span>
