    <p>When: Aug 28, 9pm Not to be missed is this panel dis­cus­sion be­tween South Korean de­signer Minju Kim, win­ner of the Net­flix’s re­al­ity com­pe­ti­tion Next In Fash­ion, and Ms Pek Lay Peng, owner of lo­cal multi-la­bel store So­ci­etyA, where Kim’s col­lec­tion is stocked.</p>
    <p>They will ad­dress top­ics such as how to mar­ket Asian de­sign­ers and whether it is Asia’s time to shine in the in­dus­try.</p>
    <p>Ex­pect a “no-holds-barred” dis­cus­sion, says Boey, a self-con­fessed fan of Kim.</p>
    <p>“If we need to tell an un­com­fort­able truth, we will, be­cause that’s the re­al­ity right now.</p>
    <p>(We want) to en­cour­age peo­ple to think and start their own dis­cus­sions,” he says.</p>


